{"type": "article", "id": 16231, "title": "SŌTŌ 米酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-19T06:00:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104227hCTWsaL8fDpeKnov.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本一个新的品牌<span></span> SŌTŌ <span></span>为了远销国外吸引更多顾客，请来了美国纽约的设计师  Joe Doucet 做的包装设计。里面装的米酒产于日本中部的新泻县，运用了常见的玻璃瓶，在白色的标签纸上印着黑色的字，错落排布，清爽极简。米酒在运输中需要冷藏，除了在瓶子外面裹上防水标签，还在玻璃瓶盖上加了一块牛仔布料，既可以擦拭瓶子外因冷藏带来的水珠也可以垫在瓶子下面防滑。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143554em12jqAgozE0Xkyn.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143555R8nVovtYrzTM04Dc.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143556sZntMaxEvChj6yUd.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143556igSOnre1byI7mkzo.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"602\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.64316239\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}